## Self-Test Results

- [x] `index.html` and `product.html` present, no em/en dashes found (verified via grep + Python scan)
- [x] 12 Picsum thumbnail URLs wired (seed: art1..art12, 450x560)
- [x] Horizontal scroll: drag (mousedown/mousemove, 1.5x multiplier), prev/next arrows (scrollBy card-width), vertical wheel remapped
- [x] Product page: `getPrintById(id)` parses `?id=` param; graceful 404 fallback if id missing
- [x] Size selector: 4 buttons (8x10, 12x16, 16x20, 24x30), active state toggles, `priceForSize` recomputes on click
- [x] Add to cart: pushes `{ printId, title, size, price }` to `localStorage.art_cart`, `updateBadge()` runs on both pages
- [x] Checkout gated: `doCheckout()` checks `sessionStorage.art_jwt`; if missing, calls `showLoginModal(cb)` then retries checkout in the callback
- [x] Login POST target: `https://api.michaelwegter.com/art-store/login` -- blueprint mounted at `/art-store`
- [x] Checkout POST target: `https://api.michaelwegter.com/art-store/checkout` -- requires `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- [x] Order confirmation: `.order-id`, `.order-email`, `.order-ship` populated from API response, modal opens
- [x] Coaching panel: both pages have 3-tab drawer; tab switching works via `data-pane` attribute
- [x] Zero em dashes and en dashes in all 11 files
