## Demo URL

`https://michaelwegter.com/demos/art-print-storefront/`

Hero flow for media capture agent:
1. Load `/demos/art-print-storefront/` -- 12 cards render in horizontal scroll
2. Click next arrow -- gallery scrolls right
3. Click first card -- `product.html?id=1` loads with "Morning Fog" title and image
4. Click "16 x 20" size button -- price updates to $505
5. Click "Add to Cart" -- toast: "Morning Fog added to cart", nav badge shows 1
6. Click Cart button in header -- cart modal opens with item
7. Click "Proceed to Checkout" -- login modal appears
8. Enter any email + password, click Sign In -- login POST succeeds, order POST fires
9. Order confirmation modal opens: order ID (MW-XXXXXXXX), email, shipping estimate
10. Click "Shopify Code Panel" button -- drawer slides up showing Liquid prompt in Tab 1

