## Architecture Notes for Proposal Writer

- The coaching panel IS the differentiation: no other candidate can demo a live
  Shopify tutoring artifact that shows the exact prompt to give Claude, what to
  review in the output, and the common errors to catch.
- JWT auth is real (PyJWT, HS256, 1-hour TTL). Any credentials work -- this is
  intentional and disclosed in the login hint ("Demo: any email and password will work").
- Cart persists in `localStorage.art_cart` across page navigations (gallery to product).
- All 12 prints use Picsum Photos CC0 seeded URLs (deterministic, no API key needed).
- The demo is vanilla JS + ES modules. No bundler, no npm install. Ships as static
  files alongside the site and auto-deploys with the next push to main.

